data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. BETTER THAN NEW! This spacious home features an open & airy flow w/vaulted ceilings & great room style layout. The modern kitchen is complete with SS appliances, granite slab counters, an island/breakfast bar & a pantry. The primary suite has a lit tray ceiling, huge walk-in closet, large linen or shoe closet, ensuite bath w/dual sinks. Abundant windows w/2" blinds, CAC, laundry rm w/cabinets, loads of storage space. Fenced, covered patio & UG sprinklers too! All this on an oversized .23 acre corner lot!
